581
01:24:39,170 --> 01:24:42,399
<i>Ponte la camisa
Y la corbata... </i>

582
01:24:42,561 --> 01:24:47,133
<i>Porque el tiempo corre... </i>

583
01:24:47,298 --> 01:24:51,192
<i>¡Ponte los patines, amigo!
